## Appearance settings:

set font "monospace regular 13"

# Set background and bar colors
set default-bg "#473d4b"
set statusbar-bg "#473d4b"
set inputbar-bg "#473d4b"
set inputbar-fg "#c2b1d5"
set highlight-color "#88a9ce"
set highlight-active-color "#c2b1d5"

set continuous-hist-save

set window-title-basename
set window-title-home-tilde
set statusbar-home-tilde

set incremental-search

# Set space between pages
# set page-padding 10



## Key mappings:

map u scroll half-up
map d scroll half-down

map r reload
map R rotate

map - zoom out
map = zoom in
map + zoom reset

map i recolor
